    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience a new take on the MOBA genre!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into fast-paced 10-minute matches of non-stop skirmish filled with impactful decision-making. Playing is easy—just move, cast spells and capture treasures to secure victory! However, mastering the game will take more than luck.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/cc9de1aceaddfeb8824f7e5fbe47183c.poster.avif?t=1770840188\" width=440 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/cc9de1aceaddfeb8824f7e5fbe47183c.webm?t=1770840188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/cc9de1aceaddfeb8824f7e5fbe47183c.mp4?t=1770840188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tip the battle in your favour with elemental mayhem!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hex grid-based maps and spell arsenal consisting of 6 different elements allow you to control the battlefield with towering flames, slippery ice, soaking water, and sturdy rocks. Each element has unique spells and effects that you can combine to discover even more ways to express yourself during every single match! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/12cef151964804ac8b98d80872dce65a.poster.avif?t=1770840188\" width=440 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/12cef151964804ac8b98d80872dce65a.webm?t=1770840188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/12cef151964804ac8b98d80872dce65a.mp4?t=1770840188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your loadout and play it your way!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go solo or team up with friends in quick matches, ranked games, or custom lobbies. With a variety of elements, items and spell combinations at your disposal it's easy to come up with new ways to play! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/6d4c47fd62efc12dce909459962d186c.poster.avif?t=1770840188\" width=440 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/6d4c47fd62efc12dce909459962d186c.webm?t=1770840188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203530/extras/6d4c47fd62efc12dce909459962d186c.mp4?t=1770840188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the variety of islands or make one of your own!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hexmental has plenty of unique islands for you to explore, each completely changing how your matches unfold. And if you’re feeling creative, you can design your own island for custom games with the in-game map editor! </p>",
